---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import { redactHtml } from '../lib/redact.mjs';
---
<Base title="The Manifesto — Ice Cream to Fight With" description="What this zine is and why it exists">

  <main class="page-container">
    <header class="about-header">
      <p class="about-kicker kicker">The Manifesto</p>
      <h1>Why This Exists</h1>
      <p class="about-standfirst">A photocopied ice cream zine, stapled together irregularly by one cook with more ambition than freezer space.</p>
    </header>

    <div class="about-body">
      <p>This is a collection of ice cream recipes that actually <em>mean</em> something—flavors rooted in real places, real traditions, and real ingredients that will absolutely make you work for them.</p>

      <p set:html={redactHtml("Each of these recipes is a high-wire act of cultural translation—taking flavors that define a cuisine or a region and figuring out how to make them work in ice cream without bastardizing what makes them special. We're doing it with respect, good ingredients, and a reasonable amount of panic.")} />

      <p>Some are elegant. Some are straight-up weird. And some are flat-out endurance tests.</p>

      <p>You <strong>will</strong> <span set:html={redactHtml("fuck")} /> something up. Probably multiple somethings. That's not a failure—that's the process. The title isn't a warning, it's a promise.</p>

      <h2>Why the Black Bars?</h2>

      <p set:html={redactHtml("Good catch. The book swears—strategically, with purpose, the way a smart friend talks when the custard breaks. But the author is currently job hunting, and this site sits one click from his resume. So the website wears a tie: every profanity is redacted. Well—the vowels are. You can't prove anything. Hover over any black bar if you require certainty. If you're a recruiter—hi, welcome, please don't hover. Everything here is fucking professional.")} />

      <h2>The Difficulty Tiers</h2>

      <div class="tier-explainer">
        <div class="tier-row">
          <span class="tier-badge chill">CHILL</span>
          <p>You're making tea, basically. Simple techniques, minimal failure points, maximum reward. Start here if you've never made ice cream before.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="tier-row">
          <span class="tier-badge legit">LEGIT</span>
          <p>Real ice cream making. Custard bases, tempering, infusions. You'll learn technique here, and the results are worth the effort.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="tier-row">
          <span class="tier-badge real-deal">THE REAL DEAL</span>
          <p>Multiple components, timing choreography, and at least one moment where you'll question your life choices. The smug satisfaction when you nail it is unmatched.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="tier-row">
          <span class="tier-badge ordeal" set:html={redactHtml('A FUCKING ORDEAL')} />
          <p>Yeasted doughs, multi-day processes, rare seasonal ingredients that spoil in 48 hours. You absolute lunatic. We love you for it.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

</Base>

<style>
  .about-header {
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    padding-bottom: 1.5rem;
    border-bottom: 3px dashed var(--ink);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .about-kicker { display: block; color: var(--pink); margin-bottom: 0.6rem; }

  .about-header h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: clamp(2.3rem, 6vw, 3.8rem);
    line-height: 0.95;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 0.85rem;
    transform: rotate(-1deg);
  }

  .about-standfirst {
    font-family: var(--font-marker);
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    color: var(--pink-deep);
    max-width: 34rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .about-body {
    font-size: 1rem;
  }
  .about-body > p:first-of-type::first-letter {
    float: left;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: 3.6em;
    line-height: 0.7;
    padding: 0.04em 0.12em 0 0;
    color: var(--pink);
  }

  .about-body p {
    margin-bottom: 1.15rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .about-body h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 400;
    font-size: 1.7rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    line-height: 1.05;
    color: #16130d;
    background: var(--teal);
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.12em 0.4em 0.18em;
    margin: 2.75rem 0 1.1rem;
    transform: rotate(-1deg);
    box-shadow: 3px 3px 0 var(--ink);
  }

  .tier-explainer {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .tier-row {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    align-items: flex-start;
    padding: 1rem 1.15rem;
    background: var(--panel);
    border: 3px solid var(--ink);
    box-shadow: 4px 4px 0 var(--ink);
  }
  .tier-row:nth-child(even) { box-shadow: 4px 4px 0 var(--pink); }

  .tier-row .tier-badge {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 0.2rem;
  }

  .tier-row p {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 0.96rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
</style>
